{"type": "article", "id": 4814, "title": "Trash.zip 垃圾桶", "description": "", "date": "2014-12-30T08:10:04Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 12, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233710qIYGPQijEu2f50tO.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这款名为 Trash.zip 的垃圾桶是设计师 Fan Liyuan 在今年德国红点奖上的获奖作品。生活中我们常常遇到垃圾超出垃圾桶的承受范围这一问题，对此设计师将 Trash.zip 设计为镂空螺旋状，它可以根据放置的垃圾的量缩小或增大。按照设计师的思路，Trash.zip 能节省 40% 的材料和重量，并将垃圾的体积压缩 50% 以上，这也意味着我们使用的垃圾袋将会更少。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233708slFDxPMLKY1XiVaE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233708RNcgoQdWb1EPt4V8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233709aAOuqtTvbnB1omiW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.1671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}